CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1782839909
OL,3,CNew school building, which has never
OL,4,Cbeen used, is to be demolished and
OL,5,Crebuilt
OL,7,FA new school building at Matford Brook
OL,8,FAcademy in Exeter is to be demolished
OL,9,Fand rebuilt before it has even been
OL,10,Fused.
OL,12,FThe school opened in 2023 but the main
OL,13,Fbuilding has never been used because
OL,14,Fof structural problems. Now the
OL,15,FDepartment for Education has confirmed
OL,16,Fthat fixing it is not possible and the
OL,17,Fbest option is to demolish it and
OL,18,Fstart again.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
