OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1782839909
OL,3,CNew school building, which has never
OL,4,Cbeen used, is to be demolished and
OL,5,Crebuilt
OL,7,FIt means pupils will continue to have
OL,8,Flessons in temporary buildings until
OL,9,Fat least 2028.
OL,11,FThe school has released a statement
OL,12,Fconfirming it had received an update
OL,13,Ffrom the DfE on the future of the
OL,14,Fpermanent school building.
OL,16,FIt says: "As you know, earlier this
OL,17,Fyear the DfE appointed Kier to support
OL,18,Fwith the investigative works on site,
OL,19,Fas part of efforts to determine the
OL,20,Fmost appropriate path forward for the
OL,21,Fbuilding.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1782839909
OL,3,CNew school building, which has never
OL,4,Cbeen used, is to be demolished and
OL,5,Crebuilt
OL,7,F"Their review found the building does
OL,8,Fnot meet the required building
OL,9,Fstandards in its current form and that
OL,10,Fit is not possible to resolve these
OL,11,Fissues to the required standard. The
OL,12,FDfE has therefore decided that the
OL,13,Fbest way forward is to replace the
OL,14,Fpartially completed building with a
OL,15,Fnew school building.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1782839909
OL,3,CNew school building, which has never
OL,4,Cbeen used, is to be demolished and
OL,5,Crebuilt
OL,7,F"The DfE remains fully committed to
OL,8,Fproviding a high-quality, modern
OL,9,Fschool building for pupils, staff and
OL,10,Fthe wider community. Work is already
OL,11,Funderway by the DfE to plan the next
OL,12,Fsteps, including appointing a trusted
OL,13,Fcontractor with a strong track record
OL,14,Fto deliver the rebuild."
OL,16,FThe school has assured parents there
OL,17,Fwill be 'no change to day-to-day
OL,18,Feducation' for current and new
OL,19,Fstudents joining in September.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1782839909
OL,3,CNew school building, which has never
OL,4,Cbeen used, is to be demolished and
OL,5,Crebuilt
OL,7,FThe statement continued: "Although
OL,8,Fthis is not the news we had hoped for,
OL,9,Fand we understand that you may be
OL,10,Fdisappointed, it does provide a clear
OL,11,Fway forward for our community.
OL,13,F"Whilst there is still much detail to
OL,14,Funderstand, we're pleased to now have
OL,15,Fa path forward towards our next
OL,16,Fchapter, and which results in the best
OL,17,Fschool possible."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
