PN,40206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1782839909
OL,3,CNew school building, which has never
OL,4,Cbeen used, is to be demolished and
OL,5,Crebuilt
OL,7,FMatford Brook Academy sits in the
OL,8,Fcentre of a large housing development
OL,9,Fspanning former farmland between
OL,10,FExminster and Alphington.
OL,12,FConstruction on the site began in 2021
OL,13,Fbut by 2023 'significant' construction
OL,14,Fissues, including problems with its
OL,15,Ffoundations, became apparent.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1782839909
OL,3,CNew school building, which has never
OL,4,Cbeen used, is to be demolished and
OL,5,Crebuilt
OL,7,FIts first intake of pupils had to
OL,8,Fattend St Luke's, a few miles away. It
OL,9,Fwas claimed the new school building
OL,10,Fwas 'missing' structural bolts. The
OL,11,Fcollapse of primary contractor ISG in
OL,12,F2024 caused more delays.
OL,14,FDevon County councillor Alan Connett
OL,15,Fsaid in a post: "How on earth a brand
OL,16,Fnew, never used, school is being
OL,17,Fdemolished begs many questions about
OL,18,Fthe management and oversight of that
OL,19,Fcontract, in my view."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
