PN,40208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1782839909
OL,3,CNew school building, which has never
OL,4,Cbeen used, is to be demolished and
OL,5,Crebuilt
OL,7,FHe said he was 'delighted we at last
OL,8,Fhave an announcement on the way
OL,9,Fforward' and praised the standard of
OL,10,Feducation and high standard of the
OL,11,Ftemporary, modular buildings currently
OL,12,Fbeing used to educate students.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
